name: Munduk Hills Villas
address: Unnamed Road, Selat, Sukasada, Buleleng Regency, Bali 81152, Indonesia
review 1: Honestly I have been 5 days in PARADISE with my wife and kids! Just amazing about everything! Incredible views and super clean villa, from bedrooms to toilets! We really appreciate the kindness and hospitality of omar! We will come back without a doubt!
review 2: Simply amazing! The view is unbelievable, and the unit is very tastefully decorated and extremely fresh and clean. Would definitely recommend.
review 3: Most incredible view, so peaceful, relaxing and a 37 degree pool why not !
review 4: Awesome place, stunning view and outstanding hospitality. Perfect place to get rested.
review 5: So amazing villa .. very private - great accomodation and luxury.  Amazing housekeeper

name: SUNSET POINT
address: Q3FH+R3P, Selat, Sukasada, Buleleng Regency, Bali, Indonesia
review 1: ⚠️ Warning: DO NOT go down the mountain road here with your bike. You could die. Motorcycle brakes can fail due to heat and you will get seriously hurt or die. It has happened many times. It happened to us and thankfully we made it out safely.
review 2: The hard to drive bike to the top of the mountain in the night. The roads are narrow there are no lights so drive safe. The view is amazing it's worth the trouble to reach the top.
